ComicInfo.Summary:
MAD makes a list of all the bad things My Name Is Earl has done, and sends back what Hell's Kitchen has been cooking! MAD also spoofs children's holiday characters, class clowns and price clubs. Plus, the return of Monroe, and MAD favorites Spy vs. Spy, the Strip Club and Planet Tad!
